avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/60/426050.jpg","floor":"#6-1","id":"1442375","time":"2019-5-12 18:46","userId":"oalvay","userName":"Oalvay","userSign":"","message":"惊了云图，我的最爱，刷了五遍。不过这部评价两极化挺严重的"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/56/295606.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1442296","time":"2019-5-12 07:57","userId":"295606","userName":"absurd","userSign":"(炸雞漢堡)","message":"大多經典老番都這樣，因為他們基本都是半年番或者年番<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br><div class=\"codeHighlight\"><pre>你問這個問題純粹是看的老番不夠多</pre></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/30/263025.jpg","floor":"#7-1","id":"1442353","time":"2019-5-12 15:30","userId":"libiao","userName":"麦田米老鼠","userSign":"","message":"老番我确实看得很少<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/77/217781.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1442354","time":"2019-5-12 15:56","userId":"217781","userName":"金刚可怜","userSign":"(无可救药的百合豚)","message":"<a href=\"https://bangumi.tv/subject/77939\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">天使不设防</a><br>和高达ZZ画风差不多，前半搞笑片、后半比较忧郁。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/77/217781.jpg","floor":"#8-1","id":"1442356","time":"2019-5-12 16:07","userId":"217781","userName":"金刚可怜","userSign":"","message":"谈不上低开高走，不过前半除了卖角色外其他都是多余的，后半剧情才完全展开。结局的处理也不是特别好，算是一部喜欢的人特别喜欢，不喜欢的人完全看不下的作品。<br>神回水回差不多3/7开。<br>ep6、11、12、13、14、16、20、22、23、24都非常值得看看。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/32/233234.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1442355","time":"2019-5-12 16:02","userId":"porepoem","userName":"porepoem","userSign":"(是动画片儿不是动漫)","message":"飞跃巅峰，两部都这样。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/15/341599.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1442373","time":"2019-5-12 18:39","userId":"341599","userName":"无心","userSign":"","message":"海马","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/15/221532.jpg","floor":"#11","id